				<td colspan="2"><span>Flyboyy, if you're ebay'd at least you got the Ferrari.
<br />

<br />
Read through the songs list from level 1 up to where you are now.  See all the things bards are known for.  Develop your own ideas for what to sing when.  Test all your songs.  Some of those low level songs may be just what you need in a given situation.  Try them with and without instruments and see the difference.  Target yourself and play the damage songs... see what happens.  Watch your stats when you test the buff songs.  Practice running through PoK at top speed without hitting anyone.  Bards are fun!<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /></span></td>
			</tr><tr>
